# 1. Write an if-else statement that performs the following. If the rating is larger then eight print “this album is amazing”. \
#   If the rating is less than or equal to 8 print “this album is ok”. \
#   Test it using the rating for the album “Back in Black” that had a rating of 8.5. 
     rating = 8.5
      if (rating > 8):
        print("this album is amazing")
      else:
        print("this ablum is ok")
        
